These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-1::.
4 different pets are kept: mouse, cat, rabbit, fish
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, australian, mexican, russian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, badminton, baseball, soccer
1. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
2. the person who's sport is soccer is between the australian and the owner of the mouse##2
3. the person who's sport is badminton is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
5. the argentine is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
6. the mexican is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
7. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Pet   | mouse    | rabbit      | cat      | fish    |
| Nationality   | russian | argentine | australian | mexican |
| Sport     | badminton    | soccer       | baseball     | basketball     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-2::.
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, mexican, japanese, argentine
City: prague, venice, new-york, paris
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, romance, superhero, thriller
1. the person traveling to venice is on the far left##1
2. the thai is on the left of the argentine##1
3. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the mexican##1
4. the person watching thriller movies is on the far left##1
5. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the person traveling to new-york##3
6. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the mexican##1
7. the japanese is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |      4      |
| Nationality          | thai     | argentine     | mexican       | japanese    |
| City         | venice | new-york   | prague | paris |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller    | superhero | romance    | epic        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, fanta, soy-milk
City: prague, venice, marseilles, nizza
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, may, september, february
1. the person traveling to venice is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person traveling to marseilles##3
3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the person traveling to prague##3
4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
5. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
7. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left##1
8. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | coffee  | fanta    | soy-milk |
| City   | marseilles   | nizza  | prague  | venice    |
| Birthday         | may    | february | october | september  |

