.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-4::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: azure, turquise, purple, yellow
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, drama, family, time-travel
City: nizza, rome, london, berlin
1. the person traveling to rome is between the person watching drama movies and the person who likes azure##2
2. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
3. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
4. the person who likes purple is on the far left##1
5. the person traveling to nizza is the person who likes yellow##1
6. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
7. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
8. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the person who likes turquise##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |    3     |     4     |
| Color          | purple   | azure     | turquise | yellow |
| Movie-Genre   | family | time-travel | action   | drama     |
| City           | berlin | london      | rome     | nizza       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, card-games, gardening, video-games
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, mirinda, hot-chocolate, sprite
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, drama, romance, western
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far right##1
2. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person watching action movies##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person who's hobby is gardening and the person who's hobby is card-games##2
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
6. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
7. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is video-games##3
8. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person watching romance movies##1
9. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is video-games##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Hobby          | gardening      | video-games | card-games      | fishing |
| Beverage           | mirinda | iced-tea | sprite | hot-chocolate   |
| Movie-Genre   | romance    | western   | drama     | action   |

