.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-6::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, skydiving, chess, gardening
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, indie, reggae, rock
There are 4 different favourite colors: black, yellow, apricot, purple
1. the person who likes yellow is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
2. the person who likes apricot is the fan of rock##1
3. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who likes black##1
4. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the person who likes apricot##3
5. the fan of reggae is on the left or right of the person who likes yellow##3
6. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who likes purple##1
7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the fan of funk##1
8. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the fan of rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3       |      4       |
| Hobby           | video-games    | skydiving   | chess | gardening |
| Music-Genre   | funk     | reggae   | rock         | indie        |
| Color         | yellow | black | apricot         | purple       |

