.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, salsa, funk, soul
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, dancer, doctor, videographer
House: farmhouse, cape-cod, art-deco, townhouse
 1. the cape-cod house is on the left or right of the farmhouse house##3
 2. the art-deco house is on the left or right of the fan of funk##3
 3. the fan of soul is on the left or right of the cape-cod house##3
 4. the doctor is on the right of the art-deco house##1
 5. the art-deco house is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
 6. the fan of funk is the fan of funk##1
 7. the doctor is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
 8. the art-deco house is on the left or right of the videographer##3
 9. the farmhouse house is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
10. the dancer is on the left or right of the doctor##3
11. the dancer is the art-deco house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre         | funk    | electronic  | salsa | soul   |
| Job           | videographer | dancer   | doctor    | bartender |
| House   | townhouse      | art-deco | cape-cod | farmhouse  |

