.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-8::.
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, pineapple, watermelon, zucchini
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, folk, reggae, ambient
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, april, may, march
1. the fan of folk is on the left or right of the person eating pineapple##3
2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
4. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far right##1
5. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person eating watermelon##1
6. the fan of folk is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
7. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the person eating zucchini##3
8. the fan of reggae is on the left or right of the fan of ambient##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |      4      |
| Food          | watermelon | pineapple    | zucchini | broccoli    |
| Music-Genre         | reggae     | ambient | folk  | trance |
| Birthday   | april    | march      | july   | may         |

