.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-9::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, biathlon, weightlifting, surfing
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, dressmaker, nurse, security-guard
There are 4 different favourite colors: orange, chestnut, purple, azure
1. the dressmaker is on the far right##1
2. the person who likes purple is on the right of the doctor##1
3. the person who's sport is parkour is on the far left or far right##3
4. the nurse is on the right of the security-guard##1
5. the person who likes azure is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
7. the security-guard is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
8. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the person who likes purple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |     3     |     4      |
| Sport      | biathlon    | weightlifting            | surfing     | parkour      |
| Job           | doctor    | security-guard | nurse     | dressmaker |
| Color   | orange | purple    | chestnut | azure    |

