.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-10::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, taxi, car, bike
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, crime, horror, thriller
House: gothic-revival, farmhouse, ranch-style, wooden
1. the person watching horror movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person driving the car##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the farmhouse house##3
4. the person driving the bike is on the far right##1
5. the person watching thriller movies is the person driving the bike##1
6. the wooden house is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
7. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
8. the person driving the taxi is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Transport          | taxi   | car | tram | bike |
| Movie-Genre   | horror   | crime     | action      | thriller  |
| House   | gothic-revival | farmhouse   | ranch-style    | wooden   |

