.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-11::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, lawyer, pilot, software-developer
4 different games are played: go, snooker, billiard, poker
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, water, 7up, lemonade
1. the lawyer is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
2. the person playing go is on the left or right of the software-developer##3
3. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing poker##1
4. the pilot is on the right of the engineer##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking water##1
6. the person playing go is on the left or right of the person playing snooker##3
7. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
8. the person drinking fanta is the person playing poker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2       |     3      |   4    |
| Job           | software-developer | lawyer        | engineer   | pilot  |
| Game   | snooker             | go     | poker | billiard  |
| Beverage         | water           | lemonade | fanta   | 7up |

