.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-12::.
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, nigerian, american, german
The people have 4 different jobs:  nurse, project-manager, teacher, writer
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, grapes, watermelon, kiwi
1. the writer is on the right of the person eating watermelon##1
2. the person eating grapes is on the far left##1
3. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the project-manager##1
4. the pakistani is on the left or right of the teacher##3
5. the pakistani is on the left or right of the teacher##3
6. the person eating kiwi is between the person eating grapes and the nigerian##2
7. the pakistani is the project-manager##1
8. the american is on the left or right of the pakistani##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |        1        |     2      |     3      |   4    |
| Nationality    | pakistani   | american   | nigerian    | german |
| Job         | project-manager | teacher    | nurse      | writer |
| Food   | grapes      | kiwi | watermelon | blueberry   |

