.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-13::.
4 different games are played: whist, bridge, poker, snooker
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, traveling, woodworking, writing
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, game, cain, aristoff
1. the person playing whist is the oliveros-smoker##1
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is between the person playing bridge and the person who's hobby is writing##2
3. the person who's hobby is traveling is the aristoff-smoker##1
4. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##3
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
6. the person playing bridge is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
7. the person playing bridge is on the far left##1
8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person playing whist##1
9. the cain-smoker is the person who's hobby is writing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Game    | bridge      | whist | snooker       | poker  |
| Hobby       | woodworking | board-games | writing    | traveling |
| Cigar   | game     | oliveros         | cain | aristoff     |

