3. the fan of rock is on the far left or far right##3
4. the fan of rock is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1
5. the fan of reggae is on the left or right of the person eating lettuce##3
6. the person eating avocado is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
7. the person eating cabbage is the aristoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |      2      |     3     |     4     |
