.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-16::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, october, july, november
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, french, indonesian, polish
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, sunflower, bellflower, zinnia
1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3
2. the indonesian is on the far left##1
3. the indonesian is on the left or right of the person who growsbellflower##3
4. the person who growszinnia is between the person who's birthday is in november and the polish##2
5. the person who's birthday is in november is the argentine##1
6. the person who growszinnia is on the left or right of the argentine##3
7. the person who growssunflower is on the far left##1
8. the person who growssunflower is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |      3       |     4      |
| Birthday           | october | september | july | november      |
| Nationality   | indonesian   | polish | french       | argentine  |
| Flower           | sunflower          | bellflower  | zinnia       | daffodil |

