.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-17::.
House: gothic-revival, craftsman, modern, art-deco
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, board-games, reading, video-games
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, montecristo, aristoff, tiparillo
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the modern house##1
2. the craftsman house is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the havana-smoker##1
4. the montecristo-smoker is between the havana-smoker and the aristoff-smoker##2
5. the gothic-revival house is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far left##1
7. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left or right of the art-deco house##3
8. the modern house is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |      2      |      3      |      4      |
| House    | modern   | art-deco    | craftsman      | gothic-revival |
| Hobby       | baking  | board-games | video-games | reading     |
| Cigar   | havana | montecristo        | aristoff  | tiparillo        |

