The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, doctor, firefighter, dressmaker
There are 4 different favourite colors: black, amber, chestnut, emerald
1. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the dressmaker##1
2. the person drinking sprite is between the dressmaker and the person who likes chestnut##2
3. the person who likes emerald is on the left or right of the coach##3
4. the coach is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person drinking sprite is between the person who likes emerald and the person drinking water##2
6. the firefighter is on the far left##1
7. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person who likes amber##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |   3   |   4    |
| Beverage      | water      | sprite     | juice | coffee |
| Job   | firefighter    | doctor    | dressmaker   | coach |
| Color     | chestnut | amber | emerald   | black    |

