.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, water, tea, almond-milk
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, dancer, journalist, security-guard
4 different games are played: backgammon, billiard, snooker, domino
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
2. the person playing billiard is on the right of the bartender##1
3. the person playing snooker is the person drinking almond-milk##1
4. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking water##1
5. the person playing billiard is between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking tea##2
6. the person playing backgammon is on the left or right of the security-guard##3
7. the person playing snooker is on the far right##1
8. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the journalist##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |    3     |       4        |
| Beverage    | tea | water  | 7up  | almond-milk           |
| Job     | bartender | journalist | dancer   | security-guard |
| Game   | domino   | billiard       | backgammon | snooker  |

 